          <p>Gain insights into your spending habits and track your financial
            progress.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
          <img src="images/robot.png" alt="Chat Bot" />
          <h2>Interactive Chat Bot</h2>
          <p>Get answers to your financial questions with our interactive chat
            bot.</p>
        </div>
      </section>
